      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 05:46:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡成立特别工作组提振低迷的股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/singapore-to-set-up-review-group-to-boost-flagging-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在解决流动性不足和新股上市稀缺问题的呼声日益高涨的背景下，新加坡成立了一个工作组来重振低迷的股市，而这其实是当局对当前股市困境的默认。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/singapore-to-set-up-review-group-to-boost-flagging-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 04:30:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通将监控印度债券流动性以应对投资者限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/jpmorgan-to-monitor-indian-bond-liquidity-after-investor-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在有关部门取消了未来发行债券的资格后，摩根大通将更密切地监控其新兴市场债券指数中期限较长的印度债券的流动性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/jpmorgan-to-monitor-indian-bond-liquidity-after-investor-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 02:28:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求低迷抵消中东风险，油价有望周度下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对世界两大经济体需求的担忧盖过了地缘政治风险加剧的影响，油价连续第四周下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 23:31:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：日本股市跌幅扩大，创 2016 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着对美国经济和科技公司健康状况的担忧加剧，全球股市抛售加剧。日本股市因预期国内将进一步收紧货币政策而暴跌，进一步加剧了市场情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
